AS OF DECEMBER 31, 2014, THE COMPANY HAD TAX EFFECTED OPERATING LOSS, CAPITAL LOSS, AND TAX CREDIT CARRYOVERS FOR FEDERAL (APPROXIMATELY $24 MILLION), STATE (APPROXIMATELY $3 MILLION), AND INTERNATIONAL (APPROXIMATELY $148 MILLION), WITH ALL AMOUNTS BEFORE VALUATION ALLOWANCES. THE FEDERAL TAX ATTRIBUTE CARRYOVERS WILL EXPIRE AFTER 15 TO 16 YEARS, THE STATE AFTER

